Package: RMOPI
Title: Risk Management and Optimization for Portfolio Investment
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("wei", "ling", , "lingwei3418@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),person("yang", "liu", email = "jdcyang@126.com",role = c("aut")))
Description: This package provides plenty of functions for risk management and portfolio investment of securities with practical tools for data processing and plot. Moreover, it also includes the cos method by Fang, F. This package contains the companion code to my book 《金融风险管理与投资组合优化》.
